author: The Current
description:
Jill Riley, a host on The Current's Morning Show, talks about being able to choose the music you hear on The Current.

We’re celebrating The Current’s 20th Anniversary all year long with the music and people that made this unique Minnesota music community possible. 

Find more at https://thecurrent.org/anniversary
